    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a solid, dependable driving experience for someone looking for a practical car at a reasonable price. The exterior shows some clear signs of age, including noticeable paint fading on the roof and hood, along with several minor dents and scratches around the body. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear from regular use. Mechanically, it runs well and has been consistently serviced, though it may soon require routine maintenance for wear-and-tear items like brakes or tires. This is a great choice for a daily commuter who prioritizes function over a flawless appearance.",
