      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished example of automotive engineering and sustained reliability. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained to ensure a seamless transition for its next owner, offering a refined driving experience that balances robust performance with professional aesthetic appeal. Every component has been thoroughly evaluated to meet our standards for safety and operational integrity. We invite discerning buyers to acquire this exceptional vehicle, which represents a superior combination of durability and sophisticated design.",
