      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape for its next owner! It drives like a dream and has been super well-loved over the years. This is the perfect find for someone who wants a solid, stylish car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sorted E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8. This naturally aspirated powerplant features eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, delivering linear torque up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The power is channeled through a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox and a speed-sensing variable M-differential lock. This chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), allowing for adjustable rebound and compression settings to suit varied road surfaces. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the installation of treated rod bearings and upgraded throttle body actuators to ensure the longevity of the rotating assembly. The braking system utilizes compound cross-drilled rotors for effective heat dissipation during spirited driving. This is a purist-spec example with a rigid subframe and intact VANOS timing gear, ready for the next apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. No major mechanical issues.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
