    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving pinnacle, powered by the S54B32 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels through an M Variable Differential Lock. This chassis has been maintained with a focus on longevity, including reinforced subframe mounts and a recently serviced cooling system. The suspension geometry remains tight, offering the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance characteristic of this generation. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the engine pull is strong to the 8,000 RPM redline, and the compression remains within factory specifications.",
